- Kill yourself.

581
00:33:11,649 --> 00:33:14,575
Seems to me if you die,
everyone else will be fine.

582
00:33:15,971 --> 00:33:18,449
- You're not getting off that easy.
- Pretty please?

583
00:33:18,507 --> 00:33:21,194
I can't. Not if I can change the day.

584
00:33:21,587 --> 00:33:22,772
What about Rita?

585
00:33:23,454 --> 00:33:25,659
You think you can do
something to change her situation?

586
00:33:25,660 --> 00:33:26,597
Maybe.

587
00:33:27,763 --> 00:33:29,759
What about the guys that are after Rita?

588
00:33:29,789 --> 00:33:31,009
What do they want from you?

589
00:33:31,062 --> 00:33:33,021
