604
00:34:38,234 --> 00:34:39,860
It's for you, it's Hop.

605
00:34:41,224 --> 00:34:42,840
<i>- Hopper?</i>
- Baxter, listen good,

606
00:34:42,870 --> 00:34:44,716
'cause I only have time
to tell you this once.

607
00:34:44,769 --> 00:34:48,652
Now you gotta follow my exact
instructions, or Damien will kill you.

608
00:34:48,689 --> 00:34:50,280
- Do you understand me?
<i>- Yes.</i>

609
00:34:50,281 --> 00:34:51,405
I know about the guys

610
00:34:51,426 --> 00:34:53,396
who've been squeezing you,
in the blue sedan.

611
00:34:53,426 --> 00:34:56,002
<i>I need you to contact them for me
and tell them I'll give</i>

612
00:34:56,032 --> 00:34:57,924
them whatever they want, okay?

613
00:34:57,944 --> 00:35:00,965
I will confess,
but only if they let Rita go.

614
00:35:01,449 --> 00:35:02,814
All right, you got that?

615
00:35:02,843 --> 00:35:03,854
Yes.

616
00:35:03,969 --> 00:35:05,186
<i>You also gotta tell them... </i>

617
00:35:05,247 --> 00:35:07,429
<i>Now this is really important! Listen...</i>

618
00:35:07,954 --> 00:35:10,378
I know how serious this is.

619
00:35:10,419 --> 00:35:12,641
I understand how serious this is.

620
00:35:12,893 --> 00:35:14,227
<i>Repeat that back to me.</i>

621
00:35:15,176 --> 00:35:17,256
You understand how serious this is.

622
00:35:17,408 --> 00:35:18,458
All right.

623
00:35:18,994 --> 00:35:21,256
Now Baxter, if you screw me on this...

624
00:35:21,691 --> 00:35:22,812
you will die.

625
00:35:26,840 --> 00:35:28,274
I need to make a call.

626
00:35:31,486 --> 00:35:32,930
Detective Battle's here.

627
00:35:33,031 --> 00:35:34,284
Thanks for coming, detective.

628
00:35:34,314 --> 00:35:36,780
Rita Shelton's car was just found
on Cahuenga boulevard...

629
