serving five consecutive life sentences,

639
00:35:58,034 --> 00:36:02,751
so there's no way he could've killed
anyone in '91, let alone Garza.

640
00:36:04,408 --> 00:36:06,168
I thought they were connected.

641
00:36:06,964 --> 00:36:08,034
What about Rita?

642
00:36:12,648 --> 00:36:14,143
He deserves to know the truth.

643
00:36:14,187 --> 00:36:16,217
No, it's the only card we have.

644
00:36:22,426 --> 00:36:24,355
They found her car. She's missing.

645
00:36:27,224 --> 00:36:28,547
That was irresponsible.

646
00:36:28,598 --> 00:36:31,032
You might've just cost us two lifes.

647
00:36:31,093 --> 00:36:32,578
Now get out!

648
00:36:35,972 --> 00:36:37,235
We're ending this now.

649
00:36:37,285 --> 00:36:38,631
This is all your fault!

650
00:36:39,083 --> 00:36:41,417
All you had to do
was give me the murder book.

651
00:36:41,468 --> 00:36:44,596
You come storming on in here...
Did you even think to look in cold case?

652
00:36:44,649 --> 00:36:47,092
You know, where they keep
the unsolved murder books?

653
00:36:47,122 --> 00:36:48,719
You didn't even look, did you?

654
00:36:48,748 --> 00:36:50,654
No, I didn't go down there,
'cause you told me

