convinced her we had to go.

679
00:38:41,816 --> 00:38:43,877
She was just so torn up over it.

680
00:38:45,786 --> 00:38:47,725
That's when I knew, that's...

681
00:38:48,766 --> 00:38:50,674
that's when I knew
I'd made the right decision,

682
00:38:50,675 --> 00:38:52,480
