690
00:39:13,717 --> 00:39:15,814
No, that's why it didn't work out.

691
00:39:15,888 --> 00:39:17,252
I don't need saving.

692
00:39:17,525 --> 00:39:18,565
Never did.

693
00:39:19,126 --> 00:39:20,833
