694
00:39:20,877 --> 00:39:22,055
Stop right there, Hopper.

695
00:39:22,096 --> 00:39:25,468
I ain't going nowhere.
I'm just trying to get to cold case.

696
00:39:25,500 --> 00:39:29,735
